data.description:
Stunning 4 BR, 3 BA, 3 Car Side-Entry Garage, CBS, 2601 Sq Ft Home in the St James Golf Club. Designed with an Impressive Eight Foot Double Door Entry, 12 Foot Ceilings and Crown Moldings in the Living Areas, Coffer Ceilings in the Dining Area, and Breakfast Nook, and Tile Floors Throughout the Entire Home. Contemporary Kitchen with all Band New Stainless Steel Appliances,  42'' Maple Wood Cabinets with Granite Countertops. and Custom Under Cabinet and over Cabinet Lighting. Spacious Pantry! Master Bath Boasts a Luxurious Roman Tub, Clear Glass Enclosed Shower, Dual European style Vanities with Cultured Marble Tops and Backsplash, Moen Faucets and Designer Lighting. This Home is Situated on a Premium Lot which allows you to Entertain Year-Round with your Spacious Screened Patio Overlooking the 8th Fairway and Offering the Most Breathtaking Sunrises with an East Exposure. There is a Fenced Back Yard, with Room for a Pool. There is an Oversized 3 Car Garage with over 750 Sq Ft of Garage Space and an Extra Wide Brick Paver Extended Driveway, Walkway and Entry. Golf Cart is Negotiable. Steel Reinforced Garage Doors, Hurricane Panels for all Windows and Doors are Included.. Other exterior Features include the Mediterranean S- Style Cement Tile Roof. 
and Electric Service Panel for a Portable Generator, This Great Location offers Easy Access to Shopping and Schools and only Minutes to I95. It's a Short Drive to Treasure Coast Beaches and Fine Dining, this community Features an Elegant Gated Entrance for Added Security, a Community Pool and Spa, a Well Maintained 18 Hole Championship Golf Course, a Community Clubhouse with Fitness Room, Tennis Courts, and a Tot Lot. Don't Miss this One!
